# Solana gas-funder secret keys — one per line — used in real Solana mode.
# Multiple keys → wizard rotates round-robin (one funder per top-up).
# Format: base58 (Phantom export) OR JSON byte array (Solana CLI keypair).
# Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# The wizard creates this file when you opt in to funders during setup; you
# normally don't need to edit by hand. For a quick single-key fallback that
# works without the wizard, set SOL_GAS_FUNDER_PRIVATE_KEY in .env instead.
